tiers.ability_description: At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are First Order at the start of battle, First Order allies gain Damage Immunity for 2 turns. Whenever a First Order ally is critically hit, all First Order allies gain 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter. Whenever a First Order ally attacks out of turn, all First Order allies gain 10% Offense (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter.

First Order SF TIE Pilot has +100% Potency. While allied Supreme Leader Kylo Ren is active, First Order SF TIE Pilot can't be defeated. While First Order allies have Advantage, they ignore Taunt.

Whenever the ally in the Leader slot or First Order SF TIE Pilot is damaged while they have Advantage, Stun that enemy for 1 turn, which can't be resisted. Whenever an enemy is Stunned, First Order SF TIE Pilot's abilities gain 5% bonus damage (stacking, max 200%), he and the ally in the Leader slot gain 10% Max Health until the end of the encounter, and if the ally in the Leader slot is Supreme Leader Kylo Ren, he gains 5% Ultimate Charge. Whenever a Stunned enemy is defeated, they can't be revived, the ally in the Leader slot gains a bonus turn, and the allied Leader and First Order SF TIE Pilot recover 100% Health and Protection.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
Whenever enemies are damaged at the start of their turn, Unaligned Force User allies gain 2% Turn Meter.
Whenever Cere Junda uses a Basic ability on their turn, other allies gain +25% Turn Meter.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain Tenacity Up, they gain Protection Up (10%, stacking) for 2 turns.
At the start of each turn, if non-Galactic Legend Pirate allies have 50% or more Turn Meter, damage they receive is reduced by 75% until the end of the turn.
Whenever Enfys Nest Stuns an enemy, Enfys Nest gains 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 200%) and 5 Speed (stacking, max 50) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.
The first time each Unaligned Force User ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.

Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Commander Luke Skywalker gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.

Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User critically hits an enemy, dispel all debuffs on themself and gain 5% Turn Meter. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability against an enemy with at least 3 debuffs, reduce that enemy's Max Health by 5%. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability when they have at least 3 buffs that can be dispelled, gain 5% Max Health.
The first time each turn Rey gains Ultimate Charge, they gain an additional 6% Ultimate Charge.

Whenever Cad Bane deals damage to an enemy, remove 25% Turn Meter from that enemy.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.

Whenever Support allies grant a buff to another ally, that ally gains 10% Turn Meter (limit once per turn per ally).
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.
At the end of each turn, Healer allies recover Health and Protection equal to 50% of the amount enemies recovered that turn. This recovery can't trigger this effect on enemies.

Whenever an enemy attacks out of turn, all enemies are inflicted with Protection Disruption for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted, and all allies gain a stack of Heal Over Time and Protection Over Time for 2 turns.

At the start of Luminara Unduli's turn, all allies with less than 50% Health gain 2 stacks for Heal Over Time for 2 turns.

At the start of each encounter, grant all allies Evasion Up and Tenacity Up for 2 turns and inflict Tenacity Down and Evasion Down on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a non-support ally is critically hit, grant them Protection Up (20%, stacking, max 100%) for 2 turns.

At the start of their turn, Support allies dispel all buffs on all enemies. If Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, Potency Up, or Tenacity Up were dispelled, inflict the opposite debuff on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a Support is critically hit or inflicted with a debuff, they Stealth for 1 turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Speed Up for 2 turns.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.

At the start of battle, if there are no Galactic Legend allies, Darth Vader can't be defeated until all the other allies are defeated. Whenever an ally is defeated, Darth Vader dispels all debuffs on himself, resets all of his cooldowns, and takes a bonus turn.

During his turn, Darth Vader has +50% Health Steal for each defeated ally.

Whenever Resistance Trooper uses his Basic ability on his turn, he Exposes the target enemy for 2 turns. Whenever Resistance Trooper attacks an Exposed enemy, all other allies gain 20% Turn Meter, Resistance Trooper has a 50% chance to attack again and Expose a random enemy for 1 turn.

Whenever Resistance Trooper falls below 50% for the first time, he gains Damage Immunity and Health Steal Up for 2 turns and all other allies gain Evasion Up for 2 turns.
